snippet.title: The Spy Strikes Back ! for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

Atari 8-bit
Commodore 64


Game description:

Your task is it to collect various items, while avoiding the robot guardians.

The game features many areas, with some areas having another area in it, which you can access by going through the green doors.


What I think:

Unique game, but it lacks some action.
